title: Here We Go: RHOA & Selling Sunset
itunes:title: Here We Go: RHOA & Selling Sunset
description:
Danny recaps this week's episode of The Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured lots of Drew/Ralph red flags, Sheree's basement, and Kandi's pool troubles. Danny also briefly dips into the Selling Sunset reunion and whether or not it is jumping the shark.


Selling Sunset Chat: 19:00ish
